entries.journal_entry_description: You finally know where Hunnos Jarkey can be found. It's now time to go catch him.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Hunnos Jarkey has hired some Naboo pirates to protect and serve him. Take them down before going after Hunnos.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Defeat the Naboo Pirates Hired by Hunnos
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Hunnos Jarkey is at the Ranch. Bring him back to justice.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Report back to Lt. Khartoor. She will be eager to hear about your success.
entries.task04_comm_message_text: Greetings, trooper. Word is that Hunnos Jarkey is no longer a threat thanks to you. Report back to me and fill me in on the details of your success.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Return to Pooja and tell her about your defeat of the escaped murderer, Hunnos Jarkey. That case is now closed.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Defeat Hunnos Jarkey's hired thugs, Naboo pirate savages.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Defeat the Naboo pirate butchers who are working for Hunnos Jarkey.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Defeat the Naboo pirate muggers who were hired as muscle by Hunnos Jarkey.
